snippet.title: Ghost of Yōtei - Announce Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/ghost-of-yotei/
 
Ghost of Yōtei comes to PlayStation®5 console in 2025.
 
At the northern edge of Japan, a new warrior rises.
In 1603, Atsu sets out on a journey in the lands surrounding Mount Yōtei, an area filled with sprawling grasslands, snowy tundras, and unexpected dangers.

#ps5 #ps5games #ghostofyotei #stateofplay
